egar provides up to 120 mg of Acetic Acid per tablet from 1200 mg of Apple Cider Vinegar. This is premium formula with natural “The Mother,” easy to take, vinegar-free taste or smell, and 98% fat free. The Mother is a special fermentation process that preserves natural benefits for digestion, gut health, and immunity. Benefits - Helps control blood sugar and cholesterol levels after meals. - Support a longer-lasting feeling of fullness and reducing overall food intake - Boost probiotics for gut health and protect gastrointestinal infections Key Ingredients - Apple Cider Vinegar 1200 mg. - Consist of 120 mg. acetic acid - Contain The Mother Directions and Warnings DIRECTIONS : 1 tablet together or after the meal WARNINGS : Patients with gastritis or acid reflux should consult a doctor. Children and pregnant women should not consume. Do not use in weight control or reduction purposes. Should eat a variety of the five categories of food in appropriate proportions. STORAGE : Store below 25C, in a cool, dry place. Do not use, if cap seal is broken. Reasons to love us We have been developing science-based formulas using premium ingredients sourced from around the world for over 50 years. We believe in natural ingredients being our hero ingredients. We also pursue the latest research findings to formulate our advanced product ranges and consistently strive to anticipate consumer demand. Backed by science Premium quality formula 50+ year heritage Certified B-Corp We are B-Corp Certified B Corps are for-profit companies that meet high standards of social and environmental performance, transparency, and accountability. Swisse is a brand of H&H Group, a certified B Corp. We feel honoured to be part of a global community using business as a force for good. Frequently Asked Questions Do we need to take vitamin supplements? The key is to ensure that we get a complete and balanced intake of nutrients each day. However, due to lifestyle limitations and dietary choices, we may not a