 and phosphorous and the normal function of the immune system.","descriptionEn":"• Vitamin D contributes to normal absorption of calcium and phosphorous and the normal function of the immune system.","descriptionTh":null,"extractedText":"Blackmores 9+ Care Gold | Blackmores Club TH EN Member Sign Up Find Store Healthy Tips Products Favorite Pack World of Natural Health Natural Health Blackmores Institute About Blackmores Work with Us Ask the Expert --> News & Activities Blackmores Video News & Activities Blackmores Video Ask the Expert --> World of Natural Health Natural Health Blackmores Institute About Blackmores Work with Us Products Favorite Pack Healthy Tips Find Store  Log In Member Sign Up TH EN Health & Remedies      Health Hub       ALL Blackmores 9+ Care Gold (Dietary Supplement Product) About this product DIETARY SUPPLEMENT PRODUCT Contains 14 Nutrients + DHA & Calcium Features • Folic acid contributes to normal red blood formation. • Vitamin D contributes to normal absorption of calcium and phosphorous and the normal function of the immune system. • Iodine contributes to normal function of the nervous system, the normal production of thyroid hormones and normal thyroid function. Dosage Adult - Take 1 capsule per day with a meal, or as professionally prescribed. Active ingredients Active ingredient per capsule: Fish oil 250 mg Per capsule contains 250 mg of fish oil which provide Omega-3, including polyunsaturated fatty acids; Eicosapentaenoic acid (EPA) 25 mg, Docosahexaenoic acid (DHA) 125 mg, Saturated fat 157 mg   Calcium 120 mg From Calcium citrate 201.6 mg and Dicalcium phosphate, anhydrous 263.1 mg Magnesium 52.5 mg From Magnesium oxide 87.15 mg   Vitamin C 30 mg From Ascorbic acid 30 mg Iron 5 mg From Ferrous fumarate 15.7 mg   Beta-carotene 30% 9.6 mg Nicotinamide 9 mg   Zinc 6 mg From Zinc oxide 7.44 mg Vitamin E 5.21 IU From D-alpha-Tocopherol 87.25% 4.01 mg   Vitamin B12 1.5 mcg From Cyanocobalamin 0.1% 1.5 mg Vitamin B6 0.95 mg From Pyridoxine HCl 1.155 mg   Vitamin B1 0.567 mg From Thiamine mononitrate 0.7 mg Vitamin B2 0.7 mg From Riboflavin   Folic acid 0.2 mg Vitamin D3 5 mcg From Vitamin D3 (2000000 IU/G) 0.1 mg   Iodine 75 mcg From Potassium iodide 98.3 mcg Available size 60 capsules Cautions Cautions: Do not use if allergy to marine fish or fish oil. Warning for people who have slow blood clotting or use anti-coagulation or aspirin. Food Allergen Information: Contains Fish and soybean products To read a warning statement on a label before consuming. No effect for prevention or cure diseases. Children and pregnant women should not consume. Should eat varieties of five categories food in appropriate proportion. ฆอ. 2426/2563 | โฆษณานี้ได้รับการอนุญาตจากสำนักงานคณะกรรมการอาหารและยา Just a sore throat? 11 ways to Japanese longevity BE OUR MEMBER To get special privilege, news and promotions. To get special privilege, news and promotions. FIND A STORE Find a nearby store location --> Choose to receive our e-newsletter and get many more privileges from Blackmores -->  ฉันได้อ่านและยอมรับ  นโยบายความเป็นส่วนตัว  และ  นโยบายการให้ความยินยอม  เรียบร้อยแล้ว Get News BlackmoresTH Blackmores Thailand Healthy tips @Livemoreclub Healthy aging tips @50morefitandfun @2015 all rights reserved. Blackmores Thailand | Terms & Condition | Privacy Policies | Editorial Policy | Contact Us","productImportId":"2dfc0c62-0ccf-4b7f-aa0c-c17736d799e4","aiFactCorrection":{"notes":"Normalized names to canonical catalogue entries; retained per-capsule doses from label text; removed non-canonical ''Fish oil'' entry; no structured rows present so used extracted ingredient table","responseId":"5a4eb1fb-6557-9d98-bde9-503345c8c1f5","correctedAt":"2026-05-18T17:12:22.551Z","originalFactCount":16,"correctedFactCount":15},"activeIngredientCount":16,"structuredIngredients":[],"candidateSupplierReason":"Blackmores Thailand product pages expose structured active ingredient tables, product images and FDA advertising approval text."},"affi