onEn":"Blackmores Multivitamins for Men Tablets with sustained-release technology releases key nutrients throughout the day to provide energy and immune support.","descriptionTh":null,"extractedText":"Blackmores Multivitamins for Men Tablets All Products Shop All Products New Products Best Sellers Vegan Certified Women&#x27;s Health Men&#x27;s Health Kid&#x27;s Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition By Category Arthritis, Joint & Bone Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutritional Oils Heart Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition Kids&#x27; Health Men&#x27;s Health Multivitamins Muscle Support Nails, Hair & Skin Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health By Ingredient Calcium CoQ10 Curcumin Echinacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Multivitamins for Men Size Size 90 tablets Blackmores Multivitamins for Men is specially formulated for men over 50, delivering essential vitamins and minerals in a sustained-release tablet that provides energy support for up to 8 hours. This formula helps reduce free radical damage to body cells, support immune system health, maintain general health and wellbeing, aid metabolism, relieve tiredness, and support nervous system health. A balanced multivitamin for mature men, it supports daily vitality and wellbeing. Taken once daily with food, it fits into your wellness routine. Good health changes everything—basic support for men’s health starts here. Product Format Tablet Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Immune System Health Energy Reproductive Health Halal Certified No Added Yeast No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy Benefits & How To Use Benefits Tailormade blend of essential vitamins and minerals for men. Specifically formulated with ‘Sustained Release Technology’ to provide lasting energy for up to 8 hours a day. Supports immune system function. Supports energy production. Supports testosterone levels. Supports mental function. Supports healthy sexual function and reproductive system health. Supports general health and wellbeing. Dosage Adults Take 1 tablet once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. WARNING - If you are pregnant, or considering becoming pregnant, do not take vitamin A supplements without consulting your doctor or pharmacist. When taken in excess of 3000 micrograms retinol equivalents, vitamin A can cause birth defects. The recommended daily amount of Vitamin A from all sources is 700 microgram retinol equivalents for women & 900 microgram for men. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. Dietary supplements can only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. This product contains selenium which is toxic in high doses. A daily dose of 150 mcg for adults of selenium from dietary supplements should not be exceeded. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional Contains soya bean products and sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings Tailormade blend of essential vitamins and minerals for men. Specifically formulated with ‘Sustained Release Technology’ to provide lasting energy for up to 8 hours a day. Supports immune system function. Supports energy production. Supports testosterone levels. Supports mental function. Supports healthy sexual function and reproductive system health. Supports general health and wellbeing. Adults Take 1 tablet once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. WARNING - If you are pregnant, or considering becoming pregnant, do not take vitamin A supplements without consulting your doctor or pharmacist. When taken in excess of 3000 micrograms retinol equivalents, vitamin A can cause birth defects. The recommended daily amount of Vitamin A from all sources is 700 microgram retinol equivalents for women & 900 microgram for men. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. Dietary supplements can only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. This product contains selenium which is toxic in high doses. A daily dose of 150 mcg for adults of selenium from dietary supplements should not be exceeded. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional Contains soya bean products and sulfites. Ingredients Active ingredients per tablet: Thiamine nitrate 1.5 mg equivalent thiamine (vitamin B1) 1.2 mg Riboflavin (vitamin B2) 1.3 mg Nicotinamide 16 mg Calcium pantothenate 6.5 mg equivalent pantothenic acid (vitamin B5) 6 mg Pyridoxine hydrochloride 1.6 mg equivalent pyridoxine (vitamin B6) 1.3 mg Folic acid (vitamin B9) 400 micro