 Oil Capsules All Products Shop All Products New Products Best Sellers Vegan Certified Women&#x27;s Health Men&#x27;s Health Kid&#x27;s Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition By Category Arthritis, Joint & Bone Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutritional Oils Heart Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition Kids&#x27; Health Men&#x27;s Health Multivitamins Muscle Support Nails, Hair & Skin Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health By Ingredient Calcium CoQ10 Curcumin Echinacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Glucosamine + Fish Oil Size Size 90 capsules Blackmores Glucosamine + Fish Oil is a dual-action formula designed to support joint comfort and mobility. It helps relieve symptoms of mild arthritis, including mild joint stiffness, aches, pain, and swelling. This product also supports the development of healthy joint cartilage and helps maintain joint health, mobility, and flexibility. Taken regularly, it provides ongoing support for those managing mild osteoarthritis symptoms and contributes to general health and wellbeing. With a convenient capsule format, Blackmores Glucosamine + Fish Oil offers everyday support for joint function and movement. Good health changes everything - start with Blackmores Glucosamine + Fish Oil. Product Format Capsule Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Mild Joint Pain Joint Health Mild Arthritis No Added Yeast No Added Gluten No Added Dairy Benefits & How To Use Benefits A source of non-GMO derived glucosamine and sustainably sourced fish oil. Relieves symptoms of mild arthritis including -Mild joint aches, pains and stiffness. -Joint mobility and flexibility. -Supports joint health. Helps maintain healthy joint cartilage production. Supports general health and wellbeing. Maintains omega 3 levels in the body. Blackmores fish oils are rigorously tested for quality and highly purified. Dosage Adults Take 1 capsule three times a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, or on warfarin therapy, talk to your health professional before use. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. Dietary supplements may only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your healthcare professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains crustaceans, fish, soya bean products and sulfites. Contains approx. 177 mg sodium per daily dose. Benefits Dosage Warnings A source of non-GMO derived glucosamine and sustainably sourced fish oil. Relieves symptoms of mild arthritis including -Mild joint aches, pains and stiffness. -Joint mobility and flexibility. -Supports joint health. Helps maintain healthy joint cartilage production. Supports general health and wellbeing. Maintains omega 3 levels in the body. Blackmores fish oils are rigorously tested for quality and highly purified. Adults Take 1 capsule three times a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, or on warfarin therapy, talk to your health professional before use. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. Dietary supplements may only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your healthcare professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains crustaceans, fish, soya bean products and sulfites. Contains approx. 177 mg sodium per daily dose. Ingredients Active ingredients per capsule: Glucosamine sulfate sodium chloride 630 mg equivalent glucosamine sulfate 500 mg Fish oil - natural 500 mg containing omega-3 triglycerides 150 mg equivalent eicosapentaenoic acid (EPA) 90 mg equivalent docosahexaenoic acid (DHA) 60 mg Glucosamine + Fish Oil Reviews Let&#x27;s stay in touch Instagram Facebook TikTok LinkedIn Back To Top About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom Our Brands & Products Shop Our Products Shop Best Sellers BioCeuticals Blackmores Professional Blackmores Institute Blackmores Education Our Brands & Products Shop Our Products Shop Best Sellers BioCeuticals Blackmores Professional Blackmores Institute Blackmores Education International Markets China Hong Kong SAR iHerb Indonesia Korea Malaysia New Zealand Singapore Taiwan Region Thailand Vietnam International Markets China Ho