ne development. This is particularly important as we age, or if you have limited sun exposure. Blackmores Vitamin D3 also helps support muscle function and maintain immune system function, making it a valuable addition to your self-care routine—especially during the cooler months. It also helps maintain vitamin D levels in the body for those at risk of low vitamin D. It’s also Halal certified, making it suitable for a variety of dietary preferences and needs. Take daily with food to support your health with confidence. Blackmores Vitamin D3 1000 IU helps prevent vitamin D deficiency and helps calcium absorption. A diet deficient in calcium can lead to osteoporosis in later life. Product Format Capsule Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Bone Health Immune System Health Muscle Health Halal Certified No Added Yeast No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy Benefits & How To Use Benefits One a day capsule. Helps prevent dietary vitamin D deficiency. Supports immune system health. Helps absorption of calcium and a diet deficient in calcium can lead to osteoporosis in later life. Assists healthy bone growth. Supports muscle strength, function and health. Supports general health and wellbeing. Dosage Adults Take 1 capsule once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Dietary supplements can only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains soya bean products and sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings One a day capsule. Helps prevent dietary vitamin D deficiency. Supports immune system health. Helps absorption of calcium and a diet deficient in calcium can lead to 