r daily routine with convenient dosing - because good health changes everything. Product Format Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Collagen Formation Skin Health Women&#x27;s Health Halal Certified No Added Yeast No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy Benefits & How To Use Benefits Targeted benefits include: Improve skin elasticity. Enhance skin firmness. Improve skin hydration. Relieves skin dryness. Supports skin regeneration. Supports skin integrity. Supports collagen formation. Supports hair health. Aids connective tissue formation. Reduces free radicals formed in the body. Dosage Adults General skin health: Take 1 capsule once a day. Targeted benefits: Take 2 capsules once a day. Do not exceed 2 capsules in 24 hours. The recommended duration of use of this product must be limited to three months. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Adults only. Do not use during pregnancy or breastfeeding. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. Dietary supplements can only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains fish products, soya bean products and sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings Targeted benefits include: Improve skin elasticity. Enhance skin firmness. Improve skin hydration. Relieves skin dryness. Supports skin regeneration. Supports skin integrity. Supports collagen formation. Supports hair health. Aids connective tissue formation. Reduces free radicals formed in the body. Adults General skin health: Take 1 capsule once a day. Targeted benefits: Take 2 capsules once a day. Do not exceed 2 capsules in 24 hours. The recommended duration of use of this product must be limited to three months. Always 