ental focus when dietary intake is inadequate. Blackmores Vision Care + Energy also reduces free radicals formed in the body. The convenient capsule fits easily into daily routines alongside habits such as regular breaks and good lighting. Place it in your bag or desk drawer so consistency becomes second nature during computer-based tasks. Good health changes everything, support your vision with Blackmores Vision Care + Energy Product Format Capsule Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Eye Health Energy Halal Certified No Added Yeast No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy Benefits & How To Use Benefits Prolonged exposure from gaming/computer use can cause eyes to strain and tire. Relieves eye strain associated with screen usage. Supports healthy eyesight and eye function. Supports mental focus when dietary intake is inadequate. Supports energy levels and general health and wellbeing. Dosage Adults Take 2 capsules once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If you are pregnancy or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains soya bean products and sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings Prolonged exposure from gaming/computer use can cause eyes to strain and tire. Relieves eye strain associated with screen usage. Supports healthy eyesight and eye function. Supports mental focus when dietary intake is inadequate. Supports energy levels and general health and wellbeing. Adults Take 2 capsules once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Always read the label and follo