nd follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Nausea Halal Certified No Added Yeast No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy No Added Soya Bean Benefits & How To Use Benefits Non-drowsy formula Relieves symptoms of motion sickness. Traditionally used in Western herbal medicine to relieve: Nausea Digestive discomfort Flatulence Dosage Adults and children over 12 years Take 2-3 tablets half an hour before travelling, then 1 tablet every two hours as required. Do not exceed 5 tablets in 24 hours. Children 6-12 years Give 1 tablet half an hour before travelling, then 1 tablet every two hours as required. Do not exceed 5 tablets in 24 hours. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If symptoms persist talk to your health professional. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. Do not exceed 2 tablets in 24 hours in pregnancy. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings Non-drowsy formula Relieves symptoms of motion sickness. Traditionally used in Western herbal medicine to relieve: Nausea Digestive discomfort Flatulence Adults and children over 12 years Take 2-3 tablets half an hour before travelling, then 1 tablet every two hours as required. Do not exceed 5 tablets in 24 hours. Children 6-12 years Give 1 tablet half an hour before travelling, then 1 tablet every two hours as required. Do not exceed 5 tablets in 24 hours. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If symptoms persist talk to your health professional. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. Do not exceed 2 tablets in 24 hours in pregnancy. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications al