ily, it also helps you stay prepared throughout the year. Blackmores Echinacea Forte is ideal for individuals seeking a plant-based approach to immune support, especially when lifestyle demands may impact wellness. Product Format Tablet Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Immune System Health Common Colds & Flu Halal Certified No Added Yeast No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy Benefits & How To Use Benefits Contains standardised Echinacea purpurea . Reduces duration and symptom severity of common colds. Supports healthy immune system function. Maintains a healthy lymphatic system. Dosage Adults Take 2 tablets 3 times a day with meals, or as prescribed by a health professional. Children under 18 years Only as prescribed by a health professional. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Adults only. If symptoms persist talk to your health professional. Supplements may only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains soya bean products. Benefits Dosage Warnings Contains standardised Echinacea purpurea . Reduces duration and symptom severity of common colds. Supports healthy immune system function. Maintains a healthy lymphatic system. Adults Take 2 tablets 3 times a day with meals, or as prescribed by a health professional. Children under 18 years Only as prescribed by a health professional. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Adults only. If symptoms persist talk to your health professional. Supplements may only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your 